entries.femaleVariant: [Show photo] You the guy in this picture?
Guy in the picture – that you?
What the... How the hell'd you get that?!
Know where to even start?
Found it – 'longside Josie's banged-up bike. Tryna figure out what happened to her.
No. All I heard was when it got rough, she ran to the metro... Must've gone south, red line from Japantown... but no idea where she woulda got off.
Not much, but... still somethin'.
Found Josie. Dead. And you did it.
Josie's dead. And it's your fault.
Got any new intel?
Any new intel on Josie?
Found Josie's ride.
Found her ride. The one she stole.
Oh, so you a cop? Cut the bullshit, show me a badge.
Nope. Hundred percent civ here – just tryna put some facts together.
I were police, you'd already be on the ground, gonk. Cuffed.
The fuck are you talking about?!
You know what. You lured her into a trap. Knew your chooms were gonna zero her.
Didn't have a choice, all right? She crossed a guy at the top. I had to, understand? They woulda zeroed me!
So you had a choice.
You pathetic piece of shit.
Know what... If you'd hazed her – just pretended to be in love so you could use her – you'd just be another asswipe in a town of full of 'em.
entries.maleVariant: Ya know what... If you'd hazed her – just pretended to be in love with her so you could use her – you'd just be another asswipe in a town of full of 'em.

entries.femaleVariant: Ah, so you had a choice. Just preferred to save your own ass.
What would you've done, huh? Let 'em wipe you?
Why you think I come back here? Night after night? To admire the fuckin' view? I know what I did. Not livin' easy with it.
Boo-fuckin'-hoo.
You're a real shitbag, Jamie. Even for Night City.
Girl bled out, Jamie. Slowly. In agony. Tore her own nails off, clawin' at the asphalt. Picture that. Picture that every time you catch that chickenshit face of yours in the mirror.
Shut up! Shut up! I'll fuckin' wipe you!
But no. You really did love her. And you still helped 'em get her.
Sure. Just you try.
Something happened to her. Something bad, right?
Shit, she... The Tygers, didn't like her, OK? Told 'er to skip town. But Josie... Fuck, Josie didn't listen.
When they smashed her ride, said she'd pay them back. I begged her not to... But she klepped a bike off some boss. They chased her, there was a firefight... after that, no idea.
So yeah, I'd say somethin' bad happened. Listen... You figure anything out, anything – lemme know, OK?
We'll be in touch.
You know where to look?
Be in touch.
Nothing. Lemme guess, you neither?
OK, and Josie? Anything?
Nothin' for now. Still lookin'.
